Subject: Alias for our HOCohesity are not being captured to determine permissions
Description: Our network team is trying to determine authorities across our filer system but alias for the HOCohesity is not identified. Can we have a call with Netwrix support and our network security admin to review their needs and capability to provide the information required?
Solution_Comment__c: it was noted that the Permissions were being set at the wrong level in Cohesity platform thus the missing details in the NEA/AIC reporting.
